{"tid":325764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國、北約、三小國和波蘭密切留意中國俄羅斯的軍演","createTime":"2017-07-17T12:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T15:32:05.000Z","uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa6e4853a01e2abe6a397388b2520363a861db1","tid":325764,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"中國和俄羅斯海軍在波羅的海軍演 美國、北約、三小國和波蘭密切留意中俄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2349/d2349552.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2349%2Fd2349552.jpg&h=2f18dc9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲解放軍的南海艦隊。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯國防部近日指出，中國艦隊將於下週抵達西部城市波羅的斯克 （俄語：Балтийск），參加24到27日舉行的「海上聯合-2017」（Joint Sea-2017）中俄聯合海軍軍演。北約秘書長史托騰柏格（Jens Stoltenberg）表示，北約組織將會關注這次的軍演。<br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯《衛星通訊社（Sputnik）》15日報導，中俄的海軍屆時將會出動大約10艘各級艦艇、10餘架飛機與直升機一同參演，至於演習的內容，除了會演練反潛，防空和反艦等項目，也會進行將情況設在有船隻被海盜劫持，雙方協力出動艦艇的緊急搜救行動。<br />\n<br />\n俄國國防部指出，除了上述的演練項目之外，俄國的海軍還會對水上和空中目標進行實彈射擊。報導指出，為了這次聯合軍演，中國海軍艦隊早在6月18日就從海南島的三亞市出發。<br />\n<br />\n波羅的海最近可以說是「暗潮洶湧」，外傳北約與美軍11日在立陶宛的聯合軍演是針對俄方，現在俄羅斯又要在隔壁的波羅的斯克附近進行聯合軍演，可以說是針對意味十分濃厚。據了解，自2014年克里米亞危機爆發以後，北約與俄羅斯與關係也越演越烈，加上自去年6月以來北約不斷向波蘭和波羅的海三國增兵，導致俄羅斯與北約緊張關係現在可以說是提高到全新的一個層面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170716/967749.htm?t=「反制」北約？　俄中海軍24日將在波羅的海聯合軍演！\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170716%2F967749.htm%3Ft%3D%E3%80%8C%E5%8F%8D%E5%88%B6%E3%80%8D%E5%8C%97%E7%B4%84%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%80%E4%BF%84%E4%B8%AD%E6%B5%B7%E8%BB%8D24%E6%97%A5%E5%B0%87%E5%9C%A8%E6%B3%A2%E7%BE%85%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%B7%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%BB%8D%E6%BC%94%EF%BC%81&d=sCocSN2yEkpdpwFnpEc9JTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=33eecbd0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170716/967749.htm?t=「反制」北約？　俄中海軍24日將在波羅的海聯合軍演！</a><ins></ins>"},{"pid":"61073a6c2fabf55f85e0814d937d9616040be426","tid":325764,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:49:28.000Z","msg":"中共解放軍與俄羅斯海軍，將於七月下旬在波羅的海展開代號「海上聯合二○一七」的演習。共軍艦隊於六月十八日由海南島榆林軍港出發，旗艦是現役最新的○五二Ｄ型驅逐艦長沙號。但近日艦隊航行到地中海後，旗艦卻變成同型的「合肥」號。<span style=\"color: red;\">國軍方面消息證實，長沙艦出航後，在南沙海域發生嚴重故障，只好被迫返港</span>，改由姊妹艦上場代打。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae1659496be2e4335781cf52127ce2daa42b1c4","tid":325764,"uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://allswalls.com/images/northrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fallswalls.com%2Fimages%2Fnorthrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-1.jpg&h=8738ab03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images3.alphacoders.com/357/35709.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages3.alphacoders.com%2F357%2F35709.jpg&h=8e4aebd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.northropgrumman.com/Photos/pgM_BS-10001_016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.northropgrumman.com%2FPhotos%2FpgM_BS-10001_016.jpg&h=afe6bbd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://allswalls.com/images/northrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fallswalls.com%2Fimages%2Fnorthrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-6.jpg&h=8dfda21a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://allswalls.com/images/northrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fallswalls.com%2Fimages%2Fnorthrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-4.jpg&h=cfd8a567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nB-2 Bomber(U.S. B-2 Spirit)<br />\n<br />\n中國係時候出動烏克蘭爛船<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817dbf051be6a05c64f5a8019f246afa8b0759af","tid":325764,"uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://allswalls.com/images/northrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fallswalls.com%2Fimages%2Fnorthrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-1.jpg&h=8738ab03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images3.alphacoders.com/357/35709.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages3.alphacoders.com%2F357%2F35709.jpg&h=8e4aebd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.northropgrumman.com/Photos/pgM_BS-10001_016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.northropgrumman.com%2FPhotos%2FpgM_BS-10001_016.jpg&h=afe6bbd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://allswalls.com/images/northrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fallswalls.com%2Fimages%2Fnorthrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-6.jpg&h=8dfda21a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://allswalls.com/images/northrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fallswalls.com%2Fimages%2Fnorthrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-4.jpg&h=cfd8a567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nB-2 Bomber(U.S. B-2 Spirit)<br />\n<br />\n中國係時候出動烏克蘭爛船<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沒有烏克蘭的蘇聯和小俄羅斯(烏克蘭)的技術，中國什麼都不是"},{"pid":"fd7c27f7119192b0735a2970bbcdba3cd64735c9","tid":325764,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T14:00:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pildid.mil.ee/upload/2017/02/23/20170223122555-8c41b8a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpildid.mil.ee%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F20170223122555-8c41b8a2.jpg&h=328f9b17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a8a2719359fbe701146fe950b7e6731b6b3bc9c","tid":325764,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:22:40.000Z","msg":"以下已經係美國同北約對俄羅斯最大讓步既協議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭民族同波烏混血之「烏克蘭國家」: <br />\n利維夫(Lviv), 因為Lviv同波蘭接壤(Lviv以前係波蘭屬土) <br />\n<br />\n斯拉夫國家之「俄羅斯聯邦」: <br />\n烏克蘭Kyiv 、烏克蘭東部、烏克蘭南部、俄羅斯同白俄羅斯 <br />\n<br />\n歐洲四小龍、三小虎和歐洲守護神: <br />\n愛沙尼亞(北約同歐盟, 美國忠實盟友)、拉脫維亞(北約同歐盟, 美國忠實盟友)、立陶宛(北約同歐盟, 美國忠實盟友)同波蘭(北約同歐盟, 美國忠實盟友) <br />\n<br />\n巴幹爾半島國家: <br />\n羅馬尼亞(北約同歐盟, 美國忠實盟友)同保加利亞(北約同歐盟, 美國盟友) <br />\n<br />\n東歐國家: <br />\n斯洛文尼亞(北約同歐盟, 美國盟友)、匈牙利(北約同歐盟, 美國盟友)、捷克(北約同歐盟, 美國盟友)同斯洛伐克(北約同歐盟, 美國盟友)"},{"pid":"0dc3595e351a5e0a48ab22211bbb7a649a869ce9","tid":325764,"uid":100986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:30:12.000Z","msg":"叫三小虎同波蘭行白俄羅斯化 = 同叫三小虎同波蘭併入俄羅斯冇分別"},{"pid":"9a8083b93962f81fff1f61b8be3e84087a8ae611","tid":325764,"uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T22:20:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中共解放軍與俄羅斯海軍，將於七月下旬在波羅的海展開代號「海上聯合二○一七」的演習。共軍艦隊於六月十八日由海南島榆林軍港出發，旗艦是現役最新的○五二Ｄ型驅逐艦長沙號。但近日艦隊航行到地中海後，旗艦卻變成同型的「合肥」號。<span style=\"color: red;\">國軍方面消息證實，長沙艦出航後，在南沙海域發生嚴重故障，只好被迫返港</span>，改由姊妹艦上場代打。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯驚支那又再copy山寨J系列出黎"},{"pid":"6013d76823005b3c185be6284107b709b9ce0b74","tid":325764,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T22:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中共解放軍與俄羅斯海軍，將於七月下旬在波羅的海展開代號「海上聯合二○一七」的演習。共軍艦隊於六月十八日由海南島榆林軍港出發，旗艦是現役最新的○五二Ｄ型驅逐艦長沙號。但近日艦隊航行到地中海後，旗艦卻變成同型的「合肥」號。<span style=\"color: red;\">國軍方面消息證實，長沙艦出航後，在南沙海域發生嚴重故障，只好被迫返港</span>，改由姊妹艦上場代打。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯同白俄驚支那又再copy山寨J系列出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f