ki-foto/#foto-437065</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/666197383227797505/Pv59gCjV_400x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2F666197383227797505%2FPv59gCjV_400x400.jpg&h=13c240f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e08697256621a97420fa49a4668b99db6afc55e","tid":325764,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:21:33.000Z","msg":"愛沙尼亞~歐洲的台灣<br />\n2017/01/23 01:42:01<br />\n<br />\n<strong>愛沙尼亞人口129萬，蘇聯解體後經濟表現強勁，被稱為波羅的海之虎之一。愛沙尼亞和台灣的處境、戰略位置非常類似。歷史上，愛沙尼亞進進出出被世界列強侵略、統治。愛沙尼亞可以作台灣的借鏡。<br />\n <br />\n蘇聯在1940年強行吞併愛沙尼亞，加上隨後二戰期間被納粹德國和蘇聯破壞，愛沙尼亞經濟被削弱。戰後，蘇聯把愛沙尼亞的經濟和工業納入中央計劃範圍，蘇維埃化持續。地處波羅的海東岸，毗鄰芬蘭灣，愛沙尼亞擁有重要的戰略位置，歷史上這裡多次爆發過戰爭。1944年，伊萬哥羅德和普喬雷被佔領愛沙尼亞的蘇聯劃入俄羅斯領土。<br />\n <br />\n愛沙尼亞和台灣狀況非常類似，小國、戰略位置重要，德國和俄國的夾縫中活下來，蘇聯解體，愛沙尼亞獨立。二戰時，愛沙尼亞國內兩派，親蘇、親德互鬥、互爭、互殺，如台灣統獨兩派，如下電影 1944。 給過份偏重於親美日的台獨派借鏡！ </strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.udn.com/mobile/feb2009/89579119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.udn.com%2Fmobile%2Ffeb2009%2F89579119&d=sCocSN2yEkpdpwFnpEc9JTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b0b68bcd\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.udn.com/mobile/feb2009/89579119</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rahvaraamat.ee/images/products/000/733/418/thumbnails/view/a6b24269de82d2d2602187b583a70dae962096cb/1944-2015-brd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rahvaraamat.ee%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2F000%2F733%2F418%2Fthumbnails%2Fview%2Fa6b24269de82d2d2602187b583a70dae962096cb%2F1944-2015-brd.jpg&h=350dec0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1944 (2015) BRD<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rahvaraamat.ee/p/1944-2015-brd/733418/en?ean=4743005071380\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rahvaraamat.ee%2Fp%2F1944-2015-brd%2F733418%2Fen%3Fean%3D4743005071380&d=sCocSN2yEkpdpwFnpEc9JTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=672c97e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rahvaraamat.ee/p/1944-2015-brd/733418/en?ean=4743005071380</a>"},{"pid":"4b36a77706128bb26082785b686e74c4301ad953","tid":325764,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://allswalls.com/images/northrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fallswalls.com%2Fimages%2Fnorthrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-1.jpg&h=8738ab03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images3.alphacoders.com/357/35709.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages3.alphacoders.com%2F357%2F35709.jpg&h=8e4aebd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.northropgrumman.com/Photos/pgM_BS-10001_016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.northropgrumman.com%2FPhotos%2FpgM_BS-10001_016.jpg&h=afe6bbd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://allswalls.com/images/northrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fallswalls.com%2Fimages%2Fnorthrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-6.jpg&h=8dfda21a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://allswalls.com/images/northrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fallswalls.com%2Fimages%2Fnorthrop-grumman-b2-spirit-wallpaper-4.jpg&h=cfd8a567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://nationalinterest.org/files/styles/main_image_on_posts/public/main_images/b2_spirit_closeup.jpeg_0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnationalinterest.org%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fmain_image_on_posts%2Fpublic%2Fmain_images%2Fb2_spirit_closeup.jpeg_0.jpeg&h=776069e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nB-2 Bomber(U.S. B-2 Spirit)"},{"pid":"ba09659168f295cc256fec310c01395be8824a33","tid":325764,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4285/34955984904_204bf17689_h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2